{"tid":1409312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俾人講兩句 你班傻仔就失晒焦！！","createTime":"2019-08-04T20:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T20:27:08.000Z","uid":18730,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce832286d96dcdfaf4c31928934bf07e32d7643b","tid":1409312,"uid":18730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:23:53.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n呃到你入嚟先<br />\n<br />\n黑警咁做嘢都唔還擊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點對得住自己良心<br />\n點對得住一班為咗公義而犧牲嘅同伴</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">七大訴求我相信無一個人忘記</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家每一次行動後都會有反省嘅過程<br />\n下一次嘅目標就會更明確</span></span><br />\n對付黑警只係眾多目標之中其中一個<br />\n或者係牽連比較廣 比較難對付<br />\n但從來無人話過只可以得一個目標<br />\n加入正義一方嘅人一定會越嚟越多<br />\n一路以嚟 大家嘅效率亦越嚟越高<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我地可以做到嘅<br />\n大家亦見到其實係越嚟越多</span></span><br />\n所以我地一定要相信<br />\n相信我地嘅力量<br />\n相信旭日必然會一點一滴咁將黑夜撕破<br />\n<br />\n各位同路人<br />\n請繼續喺自己崗位努力<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">信念不滅！</span></span>"},{"pid":"971fe4931b01351065faed3cc952f8c3436819bc","tid":1409312,"uid":233477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:25:09.000Z","msg":"《三思》半夜四點 邊個未訓？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1409281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1409281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"95483280ede6f9c52be2deeda718ba3a7b45a748","tid":1409312,"uid":18730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:27:08.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"}]}